window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They thought they found heaven on earth. But their paradise becomes a nightmare when Professor Brandt Savage and his girlfriend Kira Sunlight stumble on a terrifying conspiracy​.</b><br> <br> When professor turned crime-fighter Brandt \"Doc\" Savage and his girlfriend Kira Sunlight land on a desert island in the middle of the Atlantic, they think they've found a perfect utopia. An escape from their tumultuous pasts.<br> <br> But they don't have long to enjoy their newfound peace before they are violently separated and dragged to opposite ends of the Earth.<br> <br> Doc's search for Kira takes him from the coast of Brazil to northern Europe and the jungles of the Congo, and he discovers they are entangled in a global conspiracy that is bigger he ever could have imagined.</p>"; 
